      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "For high-stakes presentations, a sharp, conservative look is key to projecting authority. Men should opt for classic, well-tailored suits in dark, solid colors, and keep their hair neatly trimmed and slicked back. Women should favor impeccably fitted professional attire, ensuring makeup is polished but understated, and hair is styled in a controlled manner. These timeless standards signal discipline and seriousness, which is what the boardroom respects.",
